The Eagles - Victim Of Love The Darkness A Compilation 2018 ak VO

The Eagles are an American rock band formed in Los Angeles in 1971.
With five number-one singles, six Grammy Awards, five American Music 

Awards, and six number-one albums, the Eagles were one of the most 

successful musical acts of the 1970s.  The Eagles are one of the world's 

best-selling bands in history, having sold more than 150 million records 

and are the highest-selling American band in U.S. history.

October 2018, The Eagles formally announced a worldwide tour and are 

to visit Europe and Oceania in early 2019. So theres that. 
Whats this?
A compilation thats not just a peaceful easy feelin. Nor is it another 

rehash of Greatest Hits(gag) We already have pages of Hits.
